All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AddBookManuallyController
The AddBookManuallyController class handles the manual addition of a book in the system.
AddBookSearchController
Controller class responsible for handling book search, display, and addition to collections.
AddCollectionController
The AddCollectionController class handles the addition of new collections in the application.
AddLenderController
The AddLenderController class manages the functionality for adding a new lender.
AlertManager
The AlertManager class is a singleton that handles the display of alert popups.
Book
The Book class represents a book entity in the library management system.
BookController
The BookController class is responsible for displaying book data within a view.
BookDAO
The BookDAO class is responsible for interacting with the database to perform CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations for Book objects.
BookDAOInterface
The BookDAOInterface defines the contract for the data access operations related to Book objects.
BookDetailsController
The BookDetailsController class is responsible for displaying detailed information about a selected book.
BookForm
The BookForm class is a parents class for AddBookManually and EditBookDetails.
BookValidation
The BookValidation class handles the verification of book credentials.
ChangePasswordController
The ChangePasswordController class handles the functionality for updating the user's password.
ChangeUsernameController
The ChangeUsernameController class handles updating the user's username.
ClientController
The ClientController class is responsible for managing the main layout of the client interface.
Collection
The Collection class represents a collection of books associated with a specific user in the library management system.
CollectionDAO
The CollectionDAO class provides data access methods for managing Collection records in the database.
CollectionDAOInterface
The CollectionDAOInterface defines the contract for data access operations related to Collection objects.
CreateAccountController
The CreateAccountController class handles the logic for creating a new user account.
DatabaseConnector
The DatabaseConnector class manages the connection to the SQLite database.
DeleteBookController
Controller class responsible for managing the deletion of books.
EditBookDetailsController
The EditBookDetailsController class manages the user interface for editing book details in the library management system.
LendingCellController
The LendingCellController class manages the UI components within each loan cell in the lending list view.
LendingPageController
The LendingPageController class manages the lending page of the application.
LibraHomeApp
The LibraHomeApp class is the main entry point for the library management system application.
Loan
The Loan class represents a loan record in the system.
LoanDAO
The LoanDAO class provides data access methods for interacting with the Loans table in the database.
LoanDAOInterface
The LoanDAOInterface defines the contract for data access operations related to Loan objects.
LoanService
The LoanService class provides services for managing loans, including loading, refreshing, adding, and removing loans.
LoanServiceInterface
The LoanServiceInterface defines the contract for mock LoanService functionality.
LoanViewController
The LoanViewController class manages the loan list view within the application.
LoginController
The LoginController class handles the login functionality of the application.
MockBookDAO
The MockBookDAO class is a mock implementation of the BookDAOInterface.
MockCollectionDAO
The MockCollectionDAO class is a mock implementation of the CollectionDAOInterface.
MockLoanDAO
The MockLoanDAO class is a mock implementation of the LoanDAOInterface.
MockLoanService
The MockLoanService class simulates the functionality of LoanService for unit testing purposes.
MockUserDAO
The MockUserDAO class is a mock implementation of the UserDAOInterface.
MyBooksController
The MyBooksController class displays the user's book collections and their associated books.
ProfileController
The ProfileController class handles displaying and updating the user's credentials.
Scraper
The Scraper class is responsible for scraping Google Books search results and detailed information about a specific book.
User
The User class represents a user entity in the library management system.
UserDAO
The UserDAO class provides data access methods for managing User records in the database.
UserDAOInterface
The UserDAOInterface defines the contract for the data access operations related to User objects.
UserManager
The UserManager class provides a singleton instance to manage user sessions in the library management system.
UserMenuController
The UserMenuController class manages the user interface for the main menu after a user has logged into the application.
ViewManager
The ViewManager class provides a singleton instance for managing views in the library management system.
